{"id": 7789, "title": "Ticket #7789: HTCondor should unique-ify PROCD_ADDRESS for us on Windows", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe default value for PROCD_ADDRESS on Windows is not specific to the instance of HTCondor that uses it.  This prevents multiple simultaneous HTCondors from working on Windows, and there's no good reason for it; the non-Windows default is instance-specific, based on the value of LOCK.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2020-Sep-29 13:20</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/6e88eb0084fd8f2a0ff7ffeb8c1e2929da287fc1\">[61367]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7789\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7789'); return false;\" title=\"HTCondor should unique-ify PROCD_ADDRESS for us on Windows\">#7789</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7726\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7726'); return false;\" title=\"Add int-to-string map of JobStatus attribute to Python bindings\">#7726</a></span>) Release notes.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2020-Aug-06 17:38</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/6bf326acfdb14238d2b6023f2c6b747252cddb5f\">[60401]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7789\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_p